Summary: Random photograph taken from my property
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking random photographs from my property of a light cloudy area and discovered the UFO when I downloaded the picture in my computer. In the first photo the object is a little left of the center of the picture. This shot has not been altered in any way. The second photo is an enlargement of the object done from the first photo.
